# converter.go
dir: pose_converter

## PROVIDES
ConvertPoseData (func), PoseData (struct)

## DEPENDS ON
encoding/json, fmt, strings

## CONSTRAINTS
- Coordinates must be float64
- Error handling is mandatory in callers
- Joint names must not be empty (validation required)
━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
ConvertPoseData converts 3D joint data to JSON.
PoseData represents 3D joint coordinates.
